opinions.text: On petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Arizona, Division One. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Court of Appeals of Arizona, Division One, for further consideration in light of new regulations promulgated by the Office of Personnel Management (OPM). See OPM, Final Rule, Federal Employees Health Benefits Program; Subrogation and Reimbursement Recovery,80 Fed.Reg. 29,203 (May 21, 2015)(5 C.F.R. 890.106).
